      "<h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-theme-text mt-12 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">The Golden Ratios of Styling &amp; Millimeter Tailoring</h3>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  True luxury is defined not by the logo printed on the label, but by the precision of the fit. Even high-street pieces can be instantly elevated to designer-level garments with simple, affordable custom adjustments. The secret weapon of every stylish woman is a trusted local tailor. Taking a few millimeters off a sleeve, cinching the waist of an oversized blazer, or hemming your favorite trousers precisely at your preferred shoe height makes a monumental difference in how a garment sits on the body and commands space.\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  When styling your outfits, remember to create breathing room. Exposing narrow points of the body—such as the wrists, neck, or ankles—helps break up heavy fabrics and adds an air of effortless grace. Simply pushing up your blazer sleeves, rolling up the cuffs of a crisp button-down, or leaving the top two buttons undone instantly transforms a formal outfit into a relaxed, modern signature look. Style is not a set of rigid constraints; it is an intuitive dance between structure and ease.\n</p>",
      "<div class=\"border border-theme-border my-12 bg-theme-tertiary p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-sm\">\n  <h4 class=\"font-serif text-xl text-theme-text uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 border-b border-theme-border pb-3\">FULL BEAUTY CURATED LIST</h4>\n  <ul class=\"list-none space-y-4 pl-0\">\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">1. L'Occitane Shea Butter Hand Cream Duo (Nordstrom Exclusive)</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">2. Westman Atelier Petite Baby Cheeks Blush &amp; Highlight Stick Duo</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">3. Bio Ionic 1.25-Inch Long Barrel Styling Iron</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">4. Yves Saint Laurent Make Me Blush &amp; Loveshine Lip Oil Gift Set</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">5. Briogeo Don't Despair, Repair! Super Moisture Conditioner</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">6. T3 AireBrush One-Step Smoothing Blow Dryer Brush</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">7. Supergoop! Unseen Sunscreen Broad Spectrum SPF 50 Duo</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">8. Augustinus Bader The Illuminating System Set</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"flex items-center justify-between text-xs sm:text-sm border-b border-theme-border/30 pb-3\">\n      <span class=\"text-theme-text font-serif\">9. Yves Saint Laurent 3-Piece Eye Set (Eyeshadow, Eyeliner, Mascara)</span>\n      <a href=\"https://go.shopmy.us/p-27453061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-accent hover:underline font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold shrink-0 ml-4\">SHOP LINK →</a>\n    </li>\n  </ul>\n</div>",
      "<h3 class=\"font-serif text-2xl sm:text-3xl text-theme-text mt-12 mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">Fiber First: The Garment Preservation Ritual</h3>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  Investing in high-quality garments is only the first step; preserving their fibers is what ensures their longevity. Harsh chemical dry cleaning and frequent hot machine washing break down delicate fibers like silk, cashmere, and wool, reducing their softness and altering their tailored shapes. To maximize the life of your wardrobe capsule, establish a mindful garment care routine.\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  Replace heavy iron pressing with a gentle handheld garment steamer. The hot steam relaxes fibers, releases creases, and sanitizes fabrics without flattening their rich, tactile textures. Store fine knitwear folded flat in drawers to prevent hanger stretching, and place cedar blocks or lavender sachets alongside them to protect raw fibers from moisture. By treating your garments with respect, you preserve their beautiful contours, save money over time, and honor the craft that went into making them.\n</p>",
      "<p class=\"text-theme-text-sub text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed\">\n  At its heart, building a timeless wardrobe is an act of deep self-respect. It is about declaring that you deserve clothing that is comfortable, durable, beautifully tailored, and perfectly aligned with who you are. By stripping away the noise of transient seasonal trends and focusing on high-integrity staples, you craft a signature style that is both highly modern and beautifully enduring.\n</p>\n<p class=\"text-theme-text text-base sm:text-lg mb-4 font-serif italic\">\n  With love and elegance,\n</p>"
